1
00:01:06,336 --> 00:01:10,778
=The Truth=

2
00:01:11,480 --> 00:01:14,136
=Episode 30=

3
00:01:20,814 --> 00:01:22,373
You're like a blind man riding a horse,

4
00:01:22,373 --> 00:01:23,734
teetering by a pool at night.

5
00:01:25,054 --> 00:01:26,974
Wandering around in this pitch darkness?

6
00:01:28,534 --> 00:01:30,454
If you actually fell down there,

7
00:01:31,853 --> 00:01:34,293
you might just reunite
with your dead bestie, Yu Xiao'ou.

8
00:01:36,413 --> 00:01:37,454
Who the heck are you?

9
00:01:38,454 --> 00:01:39,373
What do you want?

10
00:01:40,694 --> 00:01:42,133
Haven't I made myself clear?

11
00:01:44,413 --> 00:01:45,174
Fine.

12
00:01:46,493 --> 00:01:47,694
Then I'll repeat it for you.

13
00:01:49,974 --> 00:01:52,174
Tell me the truth
about Yu Xiao'ou's murder.

14
00:01:52,614 --> 00:01:54,974
I did.

15
00:01:54,974 --> 00:01:56,454
What I said is the truth.

16
00:01:57,054 --> 00:01:58,493
Zhang Wei brought the knife there.

17
00:01:58,694 --> 00:02:00,054
And he killed Xiao'ou.

18
00:02:00,054 --> 00:02:02,534
It had absolutely nothing to do with me.

19
00:02:05,653 --> 00:02:06,974
Nothing to do with you?

20
00:02:09,574 --> 00:02:11,134
Zhang Wei was your boyfriend.

21
00:02:13,174 --> 00:02:15,093
You said so yourself in the interview.

22
00:02:18,693 --> 00:02:20,253
You wanted to break up with Zhang Wei.

23
00:02:20,373 --> 00:02:22,454
Yu Xiao'ou was just mediating
between you two.

24
00:02:24,454 --> 00:02:27,134
She was killed by Zhang Wei
while trying to help and save you.

25
00:02:29,454 --> 00:02:30,533
And what did you do?

26
00:02:33,493 --> 00:02:34,253
No.

27
00:02:34,253 --> 00:02:35,334
You watched her die

28
00:02:35,773 --> 00:02:36,854
and finished her.

29
00:02:36,854 --> 00:02:37,454
No.

30
00:02:37,454 --> 00:02:38,854
And you defended the murderer.

31
00:02:38,854 --> 00:02:40,373
I didn't. No.

32
00:02:41,773 --> 00:02:43,014
I'm not like that.

33
00:02:49,014 --> 00:02:49,973
Wait.

34
00:02:49,973 --> 00:02:51,773
I'll talk. I'll tell you.

35
00:02:56,014 --> 00:02:57,134
Don't try any tricks.

36
00:03:13,134 --> 00:03:13,813
Hello?

37
00:03:14,854 --> 00:03:15,773
Is this Xia Tian?

38
00:03:17,854 --> 00:03:18,574
Hello?

39
00:03:36,184 --> 00:03:38,894
(Liu Yang)

40
00:03:38,894 --> 00:03:39,773
Captain Leng,

41
00:03:40,014 --> 00:03:42,054
Xia Tian's phone
suddenly became reachable.

42
00:03:42,493 --> 00:03:43,973
But something feels off.

43
00:03:44,216 --> 00:03:45,176
I'll transfer the call.

44
00:04:04,854 --> 00:04:06,454
Zhang Wei wasn't my boyfriend.

45
00:04:07,174 --> 00:04:08,693
He and Xiao'ou were the real couple.

46
00:04:09,693 --> 00:04:11,134
Xiao'ou's family disapproved,

47
00:04:12,174 --> 00:04:13,693
so they used me as a cover.

48
00:04:13,693 --> 00:04:15,693
They made me pretend
to be Zhang Wei's girlfriend.

49
00:04:16,294 --> 00:04:17,414
We shared a dorm room,

50
00:04:17,414 --> 00:04:18,493
and we were close friends,

51
00:04:18,493 --> 00:04:21,094
so I agreed,
thinking it wasn't a big deal.

52
00:04:22,614 --> 00:04:24,893
At first, it really wasn't a big deal.

53
00:04:25,893 --> 00:04:29,414
But later, Xiao'ou's family
started setting her up on blind dates,

54
00:04:29,414 --> 00:04:30,360
keeping pressuring her.

55
00:04:30,360 --> 00:04:32,414
And Xiao'ou had no excuse to refuse.

56
00:04:32,774 --> 00:04:34,573
So they began arguing nonstop

57
00:04:34,573 --> 00:04:35,813
and breaking up constantly.

58
00:04:36,453 --> 00:04:38,214
Until Xiao'ou ran out of patience.

59
00:04:38,774 --> 00:04:40,534
She insisted on breaking up
with Zhang Wei.

60
00:04:41,813 --> 00:04:44,414
That day, Zhang Wei said
he was returning some things

61
00:04:45,534 --> 00:04:47,054
and came to our dorm building.

62
00:04:49,333 --> 00:04:53,573
That knife was bought by Xiao'ou
during a trip they took together.

63
00:04:53,573 --> 00:04:56,773
(Ye Qian: What's going on?
Can we locate her?)

64
00:04:57,453 --> 00:04:59,094
(Si Yuanlong: Likely coercion)
I-I was in the dorm then.

65
00:04:59,094 --> 00:05:01,094
(Search team deployed)
But when I heard noises,

66
00:05:01,414 --> 00:05:02,933
I sensed something wrong and went out.

67
00:05:02,933 --> 00:05:05,734
H-He'd already... Xiao'ou was...

68
00:05:08,133 --> 00:05:08,974
Xia Tian?

69
00:05:11,333 --> 00:05:12,013
Xia Tian?

70
00:05:13,414 --> 00:05:14,214
Is it Jiang Yue?

71
00:05:15,534 --> 00:05:18,493
Jiang Yue, tell us your demands.

72
00:05:26,813 --> 00:05:29,013
You really are full of surprises.

73
00:05:32,013 --> 00:05:35,854
As a girl, you're much more capable
than those fools before you.

74
00:05:36,974 --> 00:05:40,974
I-I'm not. I'm not.

75
00:05:41,253 --> 00:05:44,493
Still playing games at this point?

76
00:05:45,133 --> 00:05:45,893
No.

77
00:05:46,054 --> 00:05:46,974
I'm not.

78
00:05:48,933 --> 00:05:51,774
There's a small motel
called Shanhu behind your school, right?

79
00:05:53,453 --> 00:05:54,693
The owner's a creep.

80
00:05:56,253 --> 00:05:58,534
He's installed hidden cameras
in the rooms

81
00:05:58,813 --> 00:06:00,253
to secretly record guests.

82
00:06:02,214 --> 00:06:05,013
And there are quite a few videos
of you and Zhang Wei in there.

83
00:06:07,294 --> 00:06:10,573
What if I sent these videos
to your parents?

84
00:06:10,573 --> 00:06:11,693
No. Please, no.

85
00:06:11,693 --> 00:06:12,414
Or your teachers?

86
00:06:12,573 --> 00:06:13,253
No.

87
00:06:13,253 --> 00:06:13,974
Maybe classmates?

88
00:06:13,974 --> 00:06:14,854
Please don't.

89
00:06:16,373 --> 00:06:18,013
If those got posted online...

90
00:06:18,013 --> 00:06:19,453
I'm begging you.

91
00:06:24,373 --> 00:06:25,654
Last chance.

92
00:06:26,693 --> 00:06:27,573
Tell me everything.

93
00:06:37,774 --> 00:06:39,854
Zhang Wei
really was Xiao'ou's boyfriend.

94
00:06:40,774 --> 00:06:41,854
I'm not lying about that.

95
00:06:45,094 --> 00:06:46,013
But what about me?

96
00:06:46,854 --> 00:06:50,373
Pretending to be Zhang Wei's girlfriend
for so long,

97
00:06:50,933 --> 00:06:53,294
we developed feelings for each other.

98
00:06:53,813 --> 00:06:54,654
What was I?

99
00:06:57,294 --> 00:06:59,813
Xiao'ou was furious
when she found out about us.

100
00:07:00,573 --> 00:07:01,974
She threatened to leave Zhang Wei.

101
00:07:01,974 --> 00:07:04,013
Fighting, breaking up.

102
00:07:04,813 --> 00:07:06,453
But Zhang Wei wouldn't accept it.

103
00:07:07,054 --> 00:07:08,054
What about that knife?

104
00:07:09,974 --> 00:07:11,813
Did Zhang Wei bring it himself?

105
00:07:12,414 --> 00:07:14,174
Or did you talk him into bringing it?

106
00:07:15,774 --> 00:07:16,534
It was...

107
00:07:17,654 --> 00:07:18,414
It was...

108
00:07:18,654 --> 00:07:19,453
Who was it?

109
00:07:23,453 --> 00:07:24,414
It was me!

110
00:07:24,414 --> 00:07:26,414
So what if it were me? It was me!

111
00:07:31,174 --> 00:07:32,414
For such a long time,

112
00:07:32,573 --> 00:07:34,573
Zhang Wei never intended
to break up with her.

113
00:07:35,013 --> 00:07:36,094
What did he take me for?

114
00:07:37,774 --> 00:07:40,813
I wanted him to take that knife
to scare Xiao'ou a little.

115
00:07:40,813 --> 00:07:42,133
I know Xiao'ou's personality.

116
00:07:42,253 --> 00:07:43,133
If he took the knife,

117
00:07:43,133 --> 00:07:44,734
she would definitely break up with him.

118
00:07:46,813 --> 00:07:50,614
But I truly never expected

119
00:07:52,534 --> 00:07:54,414
that he would use that knife.

120
00:07:55,373 --> 00:07:58,893
I never meant for him to kill Xiao'ou.

121
00:07:58,893 --> 00:08:00,654
I just wanted them to break up.

122
00:08:00,654 --> 00:08:03,253
I didn't want him to kill Xiao'ou!

123
00:08:21,253 --> 00:08:22,493
You all heard that, right?

124
00:08:24,294 --> 00:08:25,933
For someone so shameless like this,

125
00:08:26,974 --> 00:08:27,734
tell me,

126
00:08:30,133 --> 00:08:33,054
wouldn't it be too unfair
to the deceased not to punish her?

127
00:08:34,733 --> 00:08:35,453
Jiang Yue,

128
00:08:36,093 --> 00:08:37,054
don't be impulsive.

129
00:08:37,774 --> 00:08:40,213
If you have any demands,
you can tell us, okay?

130
00:08:41,213 --> 00:08:41,894
Jiang Yue?

131
00:08:58,933 --> 00:09:00,813
Hello, Wang Tong?

132
00:09:01,573 --> 00:09:03,294
Have you confirmed Xia Tian's location?

133
00:09:03,853 --> 00:09:04,632
We just got it.

134
00:09:04,632 --> 00:09:07,054
Near the Huancheng West Road
and Zhongshan Road intersection.

135
00:09:07,054 --> 00:09:08,213
We've told the local police.

136
00:09:08,534 --> 00:09:09,894
Our people are heading there now.

137
00:09:10,213 --> 00:09:10,813
Okay.

138
00:10:06,254 --> 00:10:08,213
(Yunxi City Map)
Several commercial buildings are here.

139
00:10:08,294 --> 00:10:09,933
Over here is the Ring Park.

140
00:10:09,933 --> 00:10:10,894
Nothing found there yet.

141
00:10:11,774 --> 00:10:12,774
Moving further this way,

142
00:10:12,774 --> 00:10:14,933
there are several
upscale residential communities.

143
00:10:14,933 --> 00:10:16,093
Hard for outsiders to enter.

144
00:10:16,093 --> 00:10:17,254
No discoveries there either.

145
00:10:17,534 --> 00:10:19,733
During the call,
distinct echoes were heard,

146
00:10:20,054 --> 00:10:21,453
along with an electric motor hum.

147
00:10:22,093 --> 00:10:24,534
So I believe
Xia Tian is likely in a basement.

148
00:10:24,774 --> 00:10:25,534
An air-raid shelter

149
00:10:25,813 --> 00:10:27,192
or inside an empty building.

150
00:10:28,376 --> 00:10:31,654
There are many abandoned
unfinished buildings by Ring Park.

151
00:10:32,134 --> 00:10:34,134
Notify the park management immediately.

152
00:10:34,654 --> 00:10:35,333
- Yes.
- Okay.

153
00:10:36,134 --> 00:10:36,774
Move out.

154
00:11:16,573 --> 00:11:17,213
Liu Yang.

155
00:11:51,374 --> 00:11:52,294
Get the power back!

156
00:11:58,933 --> 00:11:59,613
Liu Yang.

157
00:12:14,424 --> 00:12:16,696
(Fingerprint comparison
in progress. Please wait)

158
00:12:24,920 --> 00:12:25,848
(Target fingerprint
matches the original one)

159
00:12:36,774 --> 00:12:37,294
Hello?

160
00:12:38,174 --> 00:12:39,093
The results are in.

161
00:12:39,453 --> 00:12:40,453
It's formaldehyde.

162
00:12:42,853 --> 00:12:44,654
According to the technicians' analysis,

163
00:12:45,134 --> 00:12:46,444
the fingerprints in the basement

164
00:12:46,872 --> 00:12:49,496
match those found in the previous cases.

165
00:12:50,333 --> 00:12:52,174
DNA testing identified it as male.

166
00:12:53,014 --> 00:12:54,813
A small amount of formaldehyde
was found too.

167
00:12:56,534 --> 00:12:57,933
Since the prints match,

168
00:12:58,014 --> 00:13:03,174
why wasn't formaldehyde found
on the prints from the earlier cases?

169
00:13:03,894 --> 00:13:05,054
The technicians said

170
00:13:05,054 --> 00:13:06,933
formaldehyde evaporates quickly.

171
00:13:07,573 --> 00:13:09,534
After a long time,
it becomes undetectable.

172
00:13:09,693 --> 00:13:13,414
They were able to detect it this time
because they got there promptly.

173
00:13:14,093 --> 00:13:15,213
What about the victim?

174
00:13:15,333 --> 00:13:16,174
Still in surgery.

175
00:13:17,174 --> 00:13:20,693
Can we now confirm
the suspect is Jiang Yue?

176
00:13:21,134 --> 00:13:22,494
He didn't deny it.

177
00:13:22,774 --> 00:13:25,813
But we can only know for sure
if he's Jiang Yue after we find him.

178
00:13:25,933 --> 00:13:26,853
Any leads?

179
00:13:28,213 --> 00:13:30,174
We have very few leads.

180
00:13:31,534 --> 00:13:35,613
If he's gone into hiding,
he'll be hard to find.

181
00:13:39,294 --> 00:13:40,014
Come in.

182
00:13:43,333 --> 00:13:44,494
Ye, come on in.

183
00:13:45,774 --> 00:13:46,693
Jiang Yue has surfaced.

184
00:13:51,933 --> 00:13:53,733
This is the latest post on the forum.

185
00:13:54,294 --> 00:13:55,352
(Justice Comes. I Saw Their Death Throes...)
The poster published

186
00:13:55,352 --> 00:13:57,014
crime scene photos
from those five cases,

187
00:13:57,294 --> 00:13:58,973
claiming they were all his doing.

188
00:14:00,534 --> 00:14:04,014
He poses as a righteous avenger
under the guise of justice

189
00:14:04,254 --> 00:14:05,294
to stir public sentiment.

190
00:14:06,093 --> 00:14:08,453
He also posted confession videos
from the five individuals.

191
00:14:10,613 --> 00:14:14,168
The post shot
to the top of the charts instantly,

192
00:14:14,168 --> 00:14:15,672
with hundreds of thousands of hits.

193
00:14:15,973 --> 00:14:18,774
Although the forum quickly locked
and hid the post,

194
00:14:18,774 --> 00:14:20,294
it still caused quite a stir.

195
00:14:26,534 --> 00:14:29,774
It was me. I poisoned those dogs.

196
00:14:34,613 --> 00:14:36,093
I swindled people's money.

197
00:14:36,654 --> 00:14:38,654
I deserve to die horribly.

198
00:14:39,973 --> 00:14:41,374
We've already determined

199
00:14:41,374 --> 00:14:43,414
that this account
belongs to an early user.

200
00:14:43,973 --> 00:14:46,933
Records show he hasn't logged
into the site for years.

201
00:14:46,973 --> 00:14:49,014
He can't even remember
his own account password.

202
00:14:50,054 --> 00:14:55,414
And this user has no connection
to anyone involved in these five cases.

203
00:14:55,774 --> 00:14:58,213
So it's highly likely
Jiang Yue hacked his account.

204
00:15:00,654 --> 00:15:01,933
There's also a pinned comment.

205
00:15:03,853 --> 00:15:05,014
(Do you know who I am?)

206
00:15:07,294 --> 00:15:10,414
So what do you think he'll do next?

207
00:15:12,054 --> 00:15:13,093
We've confirmed

208
00:15:13,853 --> 00:15:16,453
the IP address used for the user's
last login was within the city.

209
00:15:17,254 --> 00:15:19,534
So it proves Jiang Yue
was in the city at that time.

210
00:15:21,813 --> 00:15:23,453
This guy's completely crazy.

211
00:15:23,813 --> 00:15:24,853
He's way too brazen.

212
00:15:25,693 --> 00:15:30,134
Each extra minute
he remains free poses a risk.

213
00:15:43,813 --> 00:15:45,813
Master, there's a place I need to check.

214
00:15:46,733 --> 00:15:47,733
How confident are you?

215
00:15:49,134 --> 00:15:50,054
Rest assured.

216
00:15:51,613 --> 00:15:52,414
Let's go together.

217
00:16:08,333 --> 00:16:09,453
Hand these out.

218
00:16:24,774 --> 00:16:26,573
I wanted
to get you something nice to eat.

219
00:16:26,573 --> 00:16:27,654
There's nothing here.

220
00:16:27,654 --> 00:16:28,494
Only these.

221
00:16:28,894 --> 00:16:29,654
Here, Qian.

222
00:16:30,093 --> 00:16:30,654
Thanks.

223
00:16:30,654 --> 00:16:31,374
Here, Master.

224
00:16:32,254 --> 00:16:34,134
Seriously, this place is deserted.

225
00:16:34,333 --> 00:16:35,774
Desert by day, worse by night.

226
00:16:35,774 --> 00:16:36,733
Like a ghost town.

227
00:16:39,374 --> 00:16:41,333
We've been staking this place out
for days now.

228
00:16:41,333 --> 00:16:42,494
Jiang Yue hasn't shown up.

229
00:16:42,894 --> 00:16:44,933
Could he have already fled Yunxi City?

230
00:16:45,213 --> 00:16:47,853
We've had heavy checkpoints
and sweeps these past days.

231
00:16:48,933 --> 00:16:50,894
Yet there are zero leads.

232
00:16:52,174 --> 00:16:54,774
I believe
Jiang Yue never left Yunxi City.

233
00:16:55,534 --> 00:16:56,573
If he wanted to flee,

234
00:16:57,174 --> 00:16:59,093
he could've left Yunxi first

235
00:16:59,093 --> 00:17:00,414
and then posted remotely.

236
00:17:02,254 --> 00:17:03,894
But even if he's still here,

237
00:17:04,173 --> 00:17:06,573
those fake IDs
can keep him hidden for a while.

238
00:17:06,893 --> 00:17:09,413
Why are we so sure he's here?

239
00:17:11,093 --> 00:17:13,413
Because this place
holds special meaning for Jiang Yue.

240
00:17:14,214 --> 00:17:18,734
That vacant lot by the mall
was the old fireworks factory site.

241
00:17:19,014 --> 00:17:21,254
Jiang Yue and his parents
lived here for years.

242
00:17:21,934 --> 00:17:24,734
To him, it's practically home.

243
00:17:26,093 --> 00:17:28,734
Cheng Jianmin went through
so much trouble,

244
00:17:28,734 --> 00:17:30,853
even getting people killed
for this land,

245
00:17:31,454 --> 00:17:33,133
yet it's sat empty all these years?

246
00:17:34,534 --> 00:17:36,853
Supposedly due to feng shui issues.

247
00:17:37,893 --> 00:17:39,413
Feng shui my foot.

248
00:17:40,133 --> 00:17:41,373
Pure guilty conscience.

249
00:17:42,494 --> 00:17:43,093
By the way,

250
00:17:43,173 --> 00:17:45,613
those photos and videos
in Jiang Yue's post

251
00:17:45,853 --> 00:17:47,573
have been verified by the forensic unit.

252
00:17:47,573 --> 00:17:48,333
They're authentic.

253
00:17:48,653 --> 00:17:50,373
From the clues provided by him,

254
00:17:50,454 --> 00:17:52,294
we've found Wen Yong's body.

255
00:17:52,534 --> 00:17:55,333
It was in that abandoned building
near the massage parlor,

256
00:17:55,653 --> 00:17:57,014
dumped into the foundation pit.

257
00:17:57,774 --> 00:17:59,254
It saved us some legwork.

258
00:17:59,653 --> 00:18:02,214
That guy is overconfident.

259
00:18:02,494 --> 00:18:04,173
He voluntarily uploaded evidence.

260
00:18:04,173 --> 00:18:05,454
He thinks we can't find him

261
00:18:05,454 --> 00:18:06,373
or touch him?

262
00:18:08,494 --> 00:18:10,974
Listen, this man is dangerous.

263
00:18:11,054 --> 00:18:12,294
Stay vigilant.

264
00:18:13,454 --> 00:18:14,813
Remember, safety first.

265
00:18:15,054 --> 00:18:15,974
No reckless moves.

266
00:18:16,173 --> 00:18:16,813
Am I clear?

267
00:18:17,254 --> 00:18:17,893
Understood.

268
00:19:06,520 --> 00:19:07,893
Fall back. Everyone out.

269
00:19:07,893 --> 00:19:08,494
- Yes.
- Move.

270
00:19:08,494 --> 00:19:09,333
Go.

271
00:19:10,093 --> 00:19:11,054
Get the fire department.

272
00:19:11,734 --> 00:19:12,813
Where's Ye Qian?

273
00:20:47,853 --> 00:20:48,494
Jiang Yue.

274
00:20:54,014 --> 00:20:55,694
You spoke to me on the phone that day.

275
00:20:56,254 --> 00:20:56,974
Small world.

276
00:20:58,694 --> 00:20:59,853
I've been waiting for you.

277
00:21:03,373 --> 00:21:04,454
Why are you alone?

278
00:21:07,853 --> 00:21:09,333
Your team will catch up soon.

279
00:21:10,613 --> 00:21:12,494
I suppose you have many questions.

280
00:21:13,734 --> 00:21:14,974
Since fate brought us together,

281
00:21:16,133 --> 00:21:17,613
I'll answer three.

282
00:21:18,573 --> 00:21:20,014
And truthfully.

283
00:21:20,734 --> 00:21:21,413
Deal?

284
00:21:26,093 --> 00:21:26,813
Jiang Yue,

285
00:21:27,734 --> 00:21:29,893
no one has the right to play vigilante.

286
00:21:30,534 --> 00:21:32,413
Not even if you were a victim.

287
00:21:33,173 --> 00:21:34,494
It's not too late to surrender.

288
00:21:34,494 --> 00:21:35,333
Three questions.

289
00:21:42,333 --> 00:21:43,853
You didn't kill Cheng Jianmin, right?

290
00:21:46,173 --> 00:21:47,093
Got it in one.

291
00:21:52,534 --> 00:21:53,494
What do you want?

292
00:21:54,934 --> 00:21:56,054
Name your price.

293
00:22:22,534 --> 00:22:23,774
What are you doing?

294
00:22:25,934 --> 00:22:27,294
Who are you?

295
00:22:43,294 --> 00:22:48,254
You... You're Director Jiang's son?

296
00:22:49,573 --> 00:22:52,294
You...

297
00:23:17,093 --> 00:23:18,573
Did you turn on the heating

298
00:23:19,133 --> 00:23:22,373
to throw off the time of death
and mislead the police?

299
00:23:23,494 --> 00:23:24,653
Not at all.

300
00:23:25,694 --> 00:23:28,093
I was dying for someone to find him.

301
00:23:29,454 --> 00:23:33,173
Cheng Jianmin was hated
by a lot for the heating issue.

302
00:23:34,392 --> 00:23:35,928
I tried to create more red herrings

303
00:23:36,663 --> 00:23:38,333
to speed up the investigation.

304
00:23:39,694 --> 00:23:44,214
But it turns out his own son
couldn't wait for him to die to inherit.

305
00:23:48,054 --> 00:23:49,173
Honestly, I regret it.

306
00:23:50,813 --> 00:23:52,534
I should've done it myself.

307
00:23:54,573 --> 00:23:57,694
I read the fireworks factory
explosion report.

308
00:23:58,613 --> 00:23:59,934
You were there.

309
00:24:00,934 --> 00:24:01,774
How'd you survive?

310
00:24:02,774 --> 00:24:03,813
My mom saved me.

311
00:24:04,974 --> 00:24:06,373
I was coming home from school.

312
00:24:06,774 --> 00:24:07,853
She came out to greet me.

313
00:24:12,294 --> 00:24:13,534
What's inside that box?

314
00:24:18,613 --> 00:24:20,254
That's already your fourth question.

315
00:24:21,974 --> 00:24:22,653
Take a guess.

316
00:24:24,373 --> 00:24:25,173
I think

317
00:24:26,653 --> 00:24:29,054
you deliberately left fingerprints
at every crime scene.

318
00:24:30,534 --> 00:24:32,573
Your mom
must have been important to you.

319
00:24:33,813 --> 00:24:37,573
I also believe her love for you
would never have changed.

320
00:24:38,133 --> 00:24:40,373
She wouldn't want you
to keep making mistakes like this.

321
00:25:05,813 --> 00:25:08,093
If the police had found
the crucial evidence back then,

322
00:25:09,694 --> 00:25:14,734
would my family's case
have been solved long ago?

323
00:25:17,534 --> 00:25:19,694
Protecting the lives
and property of the people

324
00:25:20,774 --> 00:25:22,734
is the duty of every police officer.

325
00:25:23,573 --> 00:25:24,934
But every case is different,

326
00:25:25,613 --> 00:25:27,413
and the difficulty
of solving them varies.

327
00:25:28,333 --> 00:25:28,974
Jiang Yue,

328
00:25:29,494 --> 00:25:30,813
please trust the police.

329
00:25:31,454 --> 00:25:33,054
Stop now. Don't make any more mistakes.

330
00:25:33,613 --> 00:25:34,214
Mistakes?

331
00:25:40,014 --> 00:25:40,813
Maybe.

332
00:25:42,774 --> 00:25:43,613
Who knows?

333
00:25:56,294 --> 00:25:57,454
We've been here for so long,

334
00:25:58,534 --> 00:26:00,413
and I haven't even
asked your name, officer.

335
00:26:02,813 --> 00:26:04,494
Ye Qian, City CID.

336
00:26:06,534 --> 00:26:07,333
Officer Ye.

337
00:26:28,934 --> 00:26:29,734
Officer Ye,

338
00:26:31,093 --> 00:26:32,373
I'll tell you another secret.

339
00:26:43,254 --> 00:26:45,093
Explosives are in
and around this building.

340
00:26:47,893 --> 00:26:49,254
All I have to do is press this.

341
00:26:52,974 --> 00:26:53,734
You all should go.

342
00:26:55,333 --> 00:26:56,254
Go far away.

343
00:26:59,173 --> 00:27:00,534
I was never a good person.

344
00:27:02,373 --> 00:27:05,613
Over these past twenty-plus years,
I've done plenty of bad, rotten things.

345
00:27:07,774 --> 00:27:09,454
I was never destined for a good end.

346
00:27:14,613 --> 00:27:16,734
I've been able to avenge my family.

347
00:27:18,392 --> 00:27:19,224
In this life,

348
00:27:21,496 --> 00:27:22,520
I have no regrets left.

349
00:27:22,520 --> 00:27:23,544
Put it down.

350
00:27:23,544 --> 00:27:24,494
Put it down!

351
00:27:27,413 --> 00:27:29,014
Looks like you don't want to leave.

352
00:29:12,093 --> 00:29:12,734
Mom!

353
00:29:13,333 --> 00:29:14,093
Mom!

354
00:29:14,214 --> 00:29:14,974
Mom!

355
00:29:15,573 --> 00:29:17,294
Mom! Wake up! Mom!

356
00:29:17,774 --> 00:29:19,534
Mom!

357
00:29:20,694 --> 00:29:22,254
Someone help!

358
00:29:22,254 --> 00:29:23,413
Help!

359
00:29:23,734 --> 00:29:26,774
Mom! Wake up! Mom!

360
00:29:26,813 --> 00:29:27,573
Mom!

361
00:29:27,694 --> 00:29:29,573
Help!

362
00:29:29,974 --> 00:29:31,694
Wake up! Mom!

363
00:29:31,813 --> 00:29:34,494
Help!

364
00:29:34,573 --> 00:29:36,974
Mom! Wake up! Mom!

365
00:30:27,494 --> 00:30:28,214
(Mom,)

366
00:30:29,893 --> 00:30:31,573
(do you see the fireworks?)

367
00:30:33,054 --> 00:30:35,613
(Aren't they as beautiful
as the ones from our factory?)

368
00:30:37,934 --> 00:30:39,613
(I've avenged you and Dad.)

369
00:30:41,333 --> 00:30:42,072
(Now)

370
00:30:43,554 --> 00:30:45,774
(it's time for me to pay the price.)

371
00:31:11,133 --> 00:31:11,813
Xia Tian,

372
00:31:12,214 --> 00:31:15,173
on the phone, you said your relationship
with Zhang Wei was fake.

373
00:31:15,373 --> 00:31:17,133
Yu Xiao'ou
was Zhang Wei's real girlfriend.

374
00:31:17,454 --> 00:31:18,653
Is this information accurate?

375
00:31:19,494 --> 00:31:20,133
Yes.

376
00:31:21,534 --> 00:31:22,694
It's all true.

377
00:31:25,173 --> 00:31:26,054
I'm guilty.

378
00:31:27,333 --> 00:31:29,093
I bear responsibility
for Xiao'ou's death.

379
00:31:30,133 --> 00:31:32,333
I regret it every single day.

380
00:31:32,974 --> 00:31:35,734
Now, whenever I close my eyes,
I see Xiao'ou's face.

381
00:31:41,093 --> 00:31:44,294
Xia Tian has admitted
to her statements made on the phone.

382
00:31:45,413 --> 00:31:48,813
She said everything
Jiang Yue made her say was true.

383
00:31:50,734 --> 00:31:52,413
As for what Xia Tian told Jiang Yue,

384
00:31:53,454 --> 00:31:54,893
whether true or false,

385
00:31:54,934 --> 00:31:56,214
it needs further investigation.

386
00:31:59,173 --> 00:32:02,853
The Yu Xiao'ou case belongs
to the neighboring province.

387
00:32:04,014 --> 00:32:06,534
We've sent them
all the relevant recordings.

388
00:32:07,133 --> 00:32:10,133
They said
they will reopen the investigation.

389
00:32:12,294 --> 00:32:13,133
That's good.

390
00:32:16,333 --> 00:32:17,873
(The Jiang Yue case led to many others)
Most crimes

391
00:32:17,873 --> 00:32:19,128
(Though Cheng Jianmin, Zhou Lianqin,)
have underlying causes.

392
00:32:19,128 --> 00:32:19,974
(Wen Yong, Liu Xiaofeng, and others are dead,
the police will reopen related cases)

393
00:32:19,974 --> 00:32:21,592
(The Cheng Jianmin cases will be reopened)
The law's purpose

394
00:32:21,592 --> 00:32:23,128
(The Zhou Lianqin fraud case will be pursued)
is to deter crimes.

395
00:32:23,128 --> 00:32:23,992
(No action will be taken
against Wen Yong and Liu Xiaofeng)

396
00:32:23,992 --> 00:32:27,014
(for their past offenses due to their deaths)
Only the law has the power to judge them.

397
00:32:46,328 --> 00:32:49,821
♪Replacing the weight of tears
with that of sweat♪

398
00:32:50,008 --> 00:32:53,615
(The Most Beautiful Sunset:
Respect and Care for the Elderly)

399
00:32:53,615 --> 00:32:58,936
♪Covering the gunshot's sound
with wounds♪

400
00:33:01,009 --> 00:33:05,863
♪No one is born unyielding and strong♪

401
00:33:06,669 --> 00:33:09,373
♪But because someone
always rushes ahead♪

402
00:33:09,373 --> 00:33:10,333
You came too?

403
00:33:10,333 --> 00:33:12,920
♪To shield us from the storm♪

404
00:33:15,576 --> 00:33:20,710
♪When every extraordinary act
becomes routine♪

405
00:33:22,680 --> 00:33:28,312
♪Just to polish the badge
upon their shoulder♪

406
00:33:30,072 --> 00:33:33,656
♪Like light surging unseen
through the night♪

407
00:33:34,808 --> 00:33:42,248
♪Converging into your form♪

408
00:33:42,573 --> 00:33:44,653
What? Aren't you happy to see me?

409
00:33:45,358 --> 00:33:48,897
♪Such dazzling glory♪

410
00:33:49,413 --> 00:33:50,294
I'm happy.

411
00:33:50,294 --> 00:33:52,440
♪Like hope♪

412
00:33:52,440 --> 00:33:56,373
♪Reaching out its arms♪

413
00:33:57,240 --> 00:33:59,892
♪Cloaked in light♪

414
00:33:59,892 --> 00:34:04,376
♪Alone, they charge ahead♪

415
00:34:04,376 --> 00:34:07,192
♪Traversing♪

416
00:34:07,192 --> 00:34:13,464
♪The battlefield of fate♪

417
00:34:13,464 --> 00:34:16,957
♪Replacing the weight of tears
with that of sweat♪

418
00:34:20,751 --> 00:34:26,072
♪Covering the gunshot's sound
with wounds♪

419
00:34:27,054 --> 00:34:28,534
You were even frowning in your dream.

420
00:34:29,213 --> 00:34:30,213
The case hit a snag?

421
00:34:32,854 --> 00:34:33,534
A bit.

422
00:34:33,805 --> 00:34:36,952
♪But because someone
always rushes ahead♪

423
00:34:36,952 --> 00:34:40,056
♪To shield us from the storm♪

424
00:34:46,374 --> 00:34:48,054
I've been waiting for your news.

425
00:34:52,494 --> 00:34:53,934
Why didn't you tell me?

426
00:34:57,208 --> 00:35:00,792
♪Like light reflected in the dust♪

427
00:35:01,944 --> 00:35:09,384
♪Sketching out your form♪

428
00:35:09,816 --> 00:35:12,494
♪Looking up♪

429
00:35:12,494 --> 00:35:16,033
♪Such dazzling glory♪

430
00:35:18,173 --> 00:35:19,494
You should smile more.

431
00:35:21,374 --> 00:35:22,693
You look best when you smile.

432
00:35:24,376 --> 00:35:27,028
♪Cloaked in light♪

433
00:35:27,028 --> 00:35:31,512
♪Alone, they charge ahead♪

434
00:35:31,512 --> 00:35:34,328
♪Traversing♪

435
00:35:34,328 --> 00:35:40,839
♪The battlefield of fate♪

436
00:36:13,560 --> 00:36:16,740
(Yunxi Port Community Senior Home:
Elders' Canteen)

437
00:36:24,600 --> 00:36:25,752
Enjoy your drinks and food.

438
00:36:25,752 --> 00:36:26,653
More dishes coming.

439
00:36:26,653 --> 00:36:27,454
Right away.

440
00:36:27,454 --> 00:36:29,014
Come on. To good health!

441
00:36:29,693 --> 00:36:30,374
Thank you.

442
00:36:30,693 --> 00:36:31,534
To good health.

443
00:36:32,632 --> 00:36:33,854
- I'll pour for you.
- Thanks.

444
00:36:33,854 --> 00:36:35,133
Bring out two more dishes.

445
00:36:35,133 --> 00:36:36,213
Sure. Coming right up.

446
00:36:36,733 --> 00:36:37,974
Ye, stir-fry this next.

447
00:36:38,133 --> 00:36:39,133
- Okay.
- Water spinach.

448
00:36:39,814 --> 00:36:40,854
That smells amazing.

449
00:36:42,213 --> 00:36:44,414
To good health.

450
00:36:44,494 --> 00:36:46,293
Sir, to your health.

451
00:36:46,573 --> 00:36:47,773
Here, let me help you.

452
00:36:47,773 --> 00:36:48,613
No need.

453
00:36:48,613 --> 00:36:49,653
Get the back of my neck.

454
00:36:49,653 --> 00:36:50,454
- It's all sweaty.
- Don't move.

455
00:36:50,454 --> 00:36:51,064
Near the hair.

456
00:36:51,814 --> 00:36:53,093
When is Xiaoyu coming?

457
00:36:54,093 --> 00:36:55,173
In about two weeks.

458
00:36:55,613 --> 00:36:58,733
I haven't properly spent time
with him on any visit.

459
00:36:59,213 --> 00:37:00,974
Where are you taking him this time?

460
00:37:01,494 --> 00:37:02,414
Haven't decided yet.

461
00:37:04,494 --> 00:37:06,814
Let's all go together next time.

462
00:37:09,494 --> 00:37:10,613
Dishes coming.

463
00:37:14,613 --> 00:37:15,334
Okay.

464
00:37:22,534 --> 00:37:23,253
Is that Han Zhao?

465
00:37:25,374 --> 00:37:25,974
Don't ask.

466
00:37:31,693 --> 00:37:32,494
Here, it's ready.

467
00:37:54,808 --> 00:37:59,992
(Your package is at the entrance)

468
00:38:29,773 --> 00:38:31,173
We're heading back tonight.

469
00:38:31,613 --> 00:38:33,974
Heard you were team-building here.
So we came to say hello.

470
00:38:35,253 --> 00:38:37,814
I've long heard
you're an excellent cook.

471
00:38:37,814 --> 00:38:39,054
I was hoping to try your food.

472
00:38:40,014 --> 00:38:41,093
Want to come in for a bit?

473
00:38:41,093 --> 00:38:42,454
No. We're in a rush.

474
00:38:42,733 --> 00:38:43,573
Maybe another time.

475
00:38:47,733 --> 00:38:48,693
Package delivered.

476
00:38:49,334 --> 00:38:50,093
We'll head off now.

477
00:40:14,414 --> 00:40:15,974
Ye Qian, hurry up.

478
00:40:16,093 --> 00:40:17,414
Just waiting on you. Come on.

479
00:40:17,414 --> 00:40:18,014
Coming.

480
00:40:42,483 --> 00:40:47,352
(Martyr Chen Yumo's Tomb)

481
00:40:47,352 --> 00:40:52,922
♪Though the story found no end,
and the promise broke♪

482
00:40:54,293 --> 00:41:00,663
♪That so-called happiness
became pain without a place to land♪

483
00:41:00,663 --> 00:41:06,715
♪All the rights and wrongs
will fade away♪

484
00:41:08,536 --> 00:41:15,224
♪I really want to know
where you landed later♪

485
00:41:15,608 --> 00:41:22,200
♪So many words I've wanted to say,
yet I find myself speechless♪

486
00:41:24,653 --> 00:41:25,374
Give it to me.

487
00:41:28,573 --> 00:41:31,653
After all these years, you still
like using ticket stubs as bookmarks.

488
00:41:33,093 --> 00:41:33,934
To keep as a memento.

489
00:41:34,944 --> 00:41:42,030
♪Maybe a scar hides deep in your heart♪

490
00:41:45,374 --> 00:41:46,613
(Later I learned)

491
00:41:47,054 --> 00:41:49,934
(Bao Hei didn't even care
about Huo's small stash of drugs.)

492
00:41:50,133 --> 00:41:53,293
(What he truly wanted
was Huo's entire network.)

493
00:41:53,693 --> 00:41:55,133
(His ambition went beyond that.)

494
00:41:55,653 --> 00:41:56,934
(He aimed to take over Nanbang)

495
00:41:56,934 --> 00:41:59,014
(to build his own
drug trafficking empire.)

496
00:41:59,653 --> 00:42:03,494
(Without the collective efforts
of numerous officers like Dan Qing,)

497
00:42:03,814 --> 00:42:06,534
(we couldn't have obtained
the core evidence against Bao Hei.)

498
00:42:07,014 --> 00:42:10,454
(Let alone precisely dismantle
his entire organization.)

499
00:42:11,014 --> 00:42:13,494
(Dan Qing once said
the night was too dark.)

500
00:42:13,693 --> 00:42:15,414
(She wished for a beam of light.)

501
00:42:15,814 --> 00:42:17,693
(But she was never one
to wait for the light.)

502
00:42:18,133 --> 00:42:20,093
(She chose
to ignite that light herself.)

503
00:42:20,454 --> 00:42:22,374
(I know she succeeded.)

504
00:42:23,014 --> 00:42:24,693
(Having always stood in the sunlight,)

505
00:42:25,054 --> 00:42:26,894
(I never truly
experienced the darkness.)

506
00:42:27,733 --> 00:42:28,733
(Because of Dan Qing,)

507
00:42:28,974 --> 00:42:30,173
(I made a resolution)

508
00:42:30,374 --> 00:42:31,573
(to spend the rest of my life)

509
00:42:31,854 --> 00:42:32,934
(delving into the darkness)

510
00:42:33,054 --> 00:42:33,934
(and fighting.)

511
00:42:34,653 --> 00:42:36,454
(She will be that light guiding me)

512
00:42:37,054 --> 00:42:38,854
(and my courage and strength.)

513
00:42:39,653 --> 00:42:42,454
(And I will never, ever give up.)

514
00:42:46,448 --> 00:42:49,941
♪Replacing the weight of tears
with that of sweat♪

515
00:42:53,735 --> 00:42:59,056
♪Covering the gunshot's sound
with wounds♪

516
00:43:01,129 --> 00:43:05,983
♪No one is born unyielding and strong♪

517
00:43:06,789 --> 00:43:09,936
♪But because someone
always rushes ahead♪

518
00:43:09,936 --> 00:43:13,040
♪To shield us from the storm♪

519
00:43:15,696 --> 00:43:20,830
♪When every extraordinary act
becomes routine♪

520
00:43:22,800 --> 00:43:28,432
♪Just to polish the badge
upon their shoulder♪

521
00:43:30,192 --> 00:43:33,776
♪Like light surging unseen
through the night♪

522
00:43:34,928 --> 00:43:42,368
♪Converging into your form♪

523
00:43:42,800 --> 00:43:45,478
♪Looking up♪

524
00:43:45,478 --> 00:43:49,017
♪Such dazzling glory♪

525
00:43:50,000 --> 00:43:52,560
♪Like hope♪

526
00:43:52,560 --> 00:43:56,493
♪Reaching out its arms♪

527
00:43:57,360 --> 00:44:00,012
♪Cloaked in light♪

528
00:44:00,012 --> 00:44:04,496
♪Alone, they charge ahead♪

529
00:44:04,496 --> 00:44:07,312
♪Traversing♪

530
00:44:07,312 --> 00:44:13,823
♪The battlefield of fate♪
